### Step 4: Validate

Run these commands in order:

1. `dotnet build sdk/playwright/Azure.ResourceManager.Playwright/`
2. `dotnet test sdk/playwright/Azure.ResourceManager.Playwright/ --filter TestCategory!=Live`
3. `eng/scripts/Update-Snippets.ps1 playwright` — injects code from `#region Snippet:` into README placeholders; verify the README diff shows the snippet code was inserted
4. `eng/scripts/Export-API.ps1 playwright` — regenerates public API listing files (run only if public API surface changed)
5. `dotnet format sdk/playwright/Azure.ResourceManager.Playwright/`

